# Crop Yield Prediction & Agricultural Data Analysis

Machine Learning project focused on agricultural data analysis, preprocessing, feature engineering, and predictive modeling.

## Workflow
1. Data Cleaning
2. Exploratory Data Analysis
3. Feature Engineering
4. Data Preprocessing
5. Model Training
6. Model Evaluation

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn
- XGBoost
- LightGBM
